text: Jessica Danielle Andrews (born December 29, 1983) is an American singer. She performs country music. Her first record Heart Shaped World was released in 1999. On April 7, 2001, her first and only number one single "Who I Am" reached the #1 spot in the country charts. She was born near Huntingdon, Tennessee. ==References== Category:Singers from Tennessee Category:Country musicians from Tennessee Category:1983 births Category:Living people
